						What This Blog Is
					</h2>

					<div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;">
						<p style="font-size: 18px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.8;">
							The Money-Printing Press is my attempt at preserving ideas that feel worth preserving while challenging the ones that don't.
						</p>
						<p style="font-size: 18px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.8;">
